{
  "stem": "27509.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I would have been sent away in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was folded in four.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He opened it in two, and closed it again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He never saw the text.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- that was on the-- I'm not sure if that was in Vilna when we went through customs, or in Moscow that we went through customs.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was one of the-- possibly in Vilna, because we were entering Soviet space.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was absolutely a miracle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I saw that men pick up this green grey piece of paper, which I recognized on the other side by the color.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I thought, that's it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the end of me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he opened it in two, and folded it back again, and put it in the papers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, as I say, the-- by the time when we came to Vladivostok, and we transferred to that cattle boat, and we had that officer with us, we still-- no one dared breathe.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we saw this man going down on the rope ladder from our boat into his accompanying boat to take him back home, when we saw him off that boat and we were on the open seas, everybody expressed a sigh of relief which was, obviously, mixed with a feeling of uncertainty, because we went-- we went into the unknown.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Today, when you say Japan and Japanese, it's-- it is part of every day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You drive Japanese cars.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You use Japanese products.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Japanese people are all around you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You encounter them. 60 Years ago, the word Japan and Japanese was just a fantasy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To come face to face with it, or to land in Japan, was just something unreal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, in fact, by the time that we survived the journey-- it was a terrible journey in the straits.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
